Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我是奧利弗•奎恩\N{\b0\fs12}My name is Oliver Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.81,0:00:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,五年裡  我被困在地獄一般的小島上\N{\b0\fs12}After five years on a hellish island,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來只有一個目標\N{\b0\fs12}I have come home with only one goal--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救我的城市\N{\b0\fs12}To save my city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但要達到目標  我不能像過去一樣成為兇手\N{\b0\fs12}But to do so, I can't be the killer I once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,為了紀念我的朋友  我只能偽裝成另一個人  \N{\b0\fs12}To honor my friend's memory, I must be someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,成為另一個存在\N{\b0\fs12}I must be something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,《綠箭俠》前情回顧\N{\b0\fs12}Previously on "Arrow"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我女兒  海倫娜\N{\b0\fs12}This is my daughter, Helena.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她父親殺了她的未婚夫的時候\N{\b0\fs12}When her father killed her fiance,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她就已經變得既黑暗又扭曲了\N{\b0\fs12}she changed into something dark and twisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸不配得到第二次機會\N{\b0\fs12}My father doesn't deserve a second chance--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,新的人生\N{\b0\fs12}a second life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這是學會控制你的力量\N{\b0\fs12}This is about learning to control your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利  結束了  我們得離開這艘船\N{\b0\fs12}Ollie, it's over! We got to get off this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,雨果•曼海姆\N{\b0\fs12}Hugo Mannheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:01:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因為詐騙  勒索  謀殺被通緝\N{\b0\fs12}Warrants out for racketeering, extortion, murder--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.21,0:01:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,黑手黨重要人物\N{\b0\fs12}The goombah trifecta.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但他從來不單獨行動  所以自己小心點\N{\b0\fs12}But he never travels alone, so watch your back,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也照顧好自己的同伴\N{\b0\fs12}watch your partner's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,出發吧\N{\b0\fs12}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.52,0:01:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你今晚幫我照看我爸\N{\b0\fs12}Thanks for helping me keep watch over my dad tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只要斯萊德還逍遙法外  我們兩家就都不安全\N{\b0\fs12}As long as Slade's out there, neither of our families are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.29,0:01:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,星城警局  把武器放在地上\N{\b0\fs12}This is the SCPD! Put your weapons on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.92,0:01:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快快快\N{\b0\fs12}Move, move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:01:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,快快快\N{\b0\fs12}Move, move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不許動\N{\b0\fs12}Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,走\N{\b0\fs12}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\b0\fs12}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,弗蘭克•波提納爾\N{\b0\fs12}Frank Bertinelli.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我女兒派你來殺我嗎\N{\b0\fs12}My daughter sent you to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  你沒事吧  受傷了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Dad, are you all right? Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事  親愛的\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, I'm fine, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不信\N{\b0\fs12}Listen, I know you don't exactly believe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,對嫌疑犯讀米蘭達法則這一套\N{\b0\fs12}in reading perps their Mirandas,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不能直接把人扔出窗外\N{\b0\fs12}but you can't just toss a guy out of a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他打傷了你\N{\b0\fs12}He shot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我這不沒事嗎\N{\b0\fs12}And I'm still here, ain't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,下次自己克制一點\N{\b0\fs12}Just next time, show a little restraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我那樣就很克制了\N{\b0\fs12}That was me showing restraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,警探  我們有另一個問題\N{\b0\fs12}Detective. We have another problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  弗蘭克•波提納爾被拘留\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, I know. With Frank Bertinelli in custody,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,女老大回市裡就只是時間問題\N{\b0\fs12}it's just a matter of time before she-ro is back in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她是誰\N{\b0\fs12}Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,海倫娜•波提納爾\N{\b0\fs12}Helena Bertinelli.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,黑手黨老大弗蘭克•波提納爾的女兒\N{\b0\fs12}Daughter of mafia boss Frank Bertinelli.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡稱呼她為  奧利弗的神經前女友\N{\b0\fs12}Or as I like to call her, Oliver's psycho ex-girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,執意報復她的父親\N{\b0\fs12}hell-bent on revenge against her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,前女友\N{\b0\fs12}Ex-girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你就聽到這個詞了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}That's what you took from that sentence?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  她為什麼這麼想殺她爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}Wait, why does she want her father killed so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他派人殺了她的未婚夫\N{\b0\fs12}He had her fiance murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-她想報復  -讓我想到了\N{\b0\fs12}- She wants payback. - Puts the many fights
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我爸爸吵過的架\N{\b0\fs12}I've had with my father in perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,過去一年裡  我一直在監視海倫娜\N{\b0\fs12}I've been keeping tabs on Helena over the past year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,最後一次出現是一個月之前\N{\b0\fs12}Last known sighting was a month ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在巴勒莫[義大利城市]\N{\b0\fs12}Palermo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她很忙啊\N{\b0\fs12}She's been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你說的"忙"\N{\b0\fs12}If by "Busy,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是指酷刑折磨和殺害那些\N{\b0\fs12}you mean torturing and killing mafiosos
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可能知道她父親下落的黑手黨成員\N{\b0\fs12}that might know where her father is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,逮捕波提納爾一事上了新聞\N{\b0\fs12}Bertinelli's arrest just hit the wires.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在海倫娜訂機票趕回來之前\N{\b0\fs12}How long do you think we
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得我們還有多少時間\N{\b0\fs12}have before Helena books a ticket back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧\N{\b0\fs12}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德  拜託\N{\b0\fs12}Slade, please--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼還不走\N{\b0\fs12}Why aren't we moving yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我們想辦法修復了船體\N{\b0\fs12}We managed to repair the hull.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是引擎損傷太嚴重了\N{\b0\fs12}But the engine is too damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-那就修好它  -我做不到\N{\b0\fs12}- So fix it. - I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道怎麼修\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know how!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去找會修的\N{\b0\fs12}Then find somebody who does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好  我是勞蕾爾  是個酒癮者\N{\b0\fs12}Hi, my name's Laurel, I'm an alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Hi, Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,今天實際上是我第二次參加會議\N{\b0\fs12}And this is actually my second meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這個...\N{\b0\fs12}It's just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這個真的太難了  因為我不知道\N{\b0\fs12}It's just so hard, because I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一整天該做什麼好\N{\b0\fs12}what to do with myself all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我是個律師\N{\b0\fs12}I'm a lawyer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾是律師\N{\b0\fs12}well, I... was...a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜歡這份工作\N{\b0\fs12}I loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想我更喜歡喝酒\N{\b0\fs12}But I guess I loved drinking more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我和你們一起在這裡時  我能做到\N{\b0\fs12}I know that I can make it down here with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不知道在外面能不能做到\N{\b0\fs12}I just...I'm not sure I can make it out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,總之\N{\b0\fs12}Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝大家讓我分享\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you for letting me share.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}唐納  來電
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}星城法院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你過來\N{\b0\fs12}Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉是那樣的結局\N{\b0\fs12}Sorry about the way things ended here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不用道歉\N{\b0\fs12}No, don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你幫了我  亞當\N{\b0\fs12}You did me a favor, Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我降到低谷的唯一方法\N{\b0\fs12}It was the only way I was going to hit bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而且\N{\b0\fs12}and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我做到了\N{\b0\fs12}and I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不如你現在幫我個忙吧\N{\b0\fs12}How about you do me a favor now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,回來工作\N{\b0\fs12}Come back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要我回來嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You want me back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我在找人處理這起剛到的案子\N{\b0\fs12}I'm looking for someone to try this case that just came in,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,老實說  我第一個想到的就是你\N{\b0\fs12}and honestly, yours was the first name that came to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,酒吧還要對我提出制裁呢\N{\b0\fs12}I'm still facing sanctions from the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我在紀律委員會有個朋友\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, I got a buddy on the disciplinary committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你擺平這件事了\N{\b0\fs12}I squared things for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚星城警局進行突襲  逮捕了弗蘭克•波提納\N{\b0\fs12}An SCPD raid last night brought in Frank Bertinelli.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他回星城來收債\N{\b0\fs12}He came back to Starling to collect on some old debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,地檢辦很明確地\N{\b0\fs12}Now, the DA's office is clear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要控告他  你來控告他\N{\b0\fs12}to prosecute him; for you to prosecute him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你的提議  亞當  但為什麼是我\N{\b0\fs12}I appreciate the offer, Adam, but why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你在創新聯合會時勝訴的\N{\b0\fs12}Well, there are rico counts
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,反詐騙腐敗組織集團犯罪案件數\N{\b0\fs12}that your time at CNRI
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你有資格勝任\N{\b0\fs12}make you ideally suited for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  這是一起案子\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, it's a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想要  它就是你的\N{\b0\fs12}If you want it, it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但前提是你得準備好\N{\b0\fs12}But only if you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}威登酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是什麼日子\N{\b0\fs12}What's the special occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我領工資了  所以\N{\b0\fs12}I got paid. So, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你覺得還不夠好\N{\b0\fs12}if you don't think it's nice enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你只能怪自己\N{\b0\fs12}you only have yourself to blame
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不給我漲工資了\N{\b0\fs12}for not giving me that raise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  我很喜歡\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,等  等我一下\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, give me-- give me a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘記訂貨了\N{\b0\fs12}I forgot to put an order in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\b0\fs12}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有新進展嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到海倫娜的未婚夫邁克爾•斯塔頓了\N{\b0\fs12}I got a line on Michael Statton, Helena's fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,費利西蒂  他死了五年了\N{\b0\fs12}Felicity, he's been dead for five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他昨晚租了\N{\b0\fs12}Which makes the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一輛車這件事尤其令人印象深刻\N{\b0\fs12}he rented a car last night very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那是海倫娜\N{\b0\fs12}That's Helena.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有車載衛星定位系統  我黑進去了\N{\b0\fs12}The car's got GPS, I hacked into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  她在往星城開\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah. She's heading straight for Starling City.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你準備好出外勤了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You ready to get back in the field?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為你永遠都不會問呢\N{\b0\fs12}I thought you'd never ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都結束了 海倫娜\N{\b0\fs12}It's over, Helena.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.37,0:07:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,從車裡出來\N{\b0\fs12}Get out of the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,槍\N{\b0\fs12}Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,別殺我\N{\b0\fs12}Don't hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,退後\N{\b0\fs12}Stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,退後\N{\b0\fs12}Stand...down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-別殺我  -閃電\N{\b0\fs12}- Don't hurt me! - Speedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了\N{\b0\fs12}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是海倫娜佈置的誘餌\N{\b0\fs12}He's just Helena's decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,有個小妞給我錢讓我開這輛車兜風\N{\b0\fs12}Some chick just paid me to take the car for a joy ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我發誓\N{\b0\fs12}I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,求你們不要殺我\N{\b0\fs12}Please don't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我下個月就要結婚了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm getting married next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,開你的車\N{\b0\fs12}Just drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,據星城警局的線索  載海倫娜進城的人\N{\b0\fs12}According to the SCPD, the guy that gave Helena
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是一名在星城大學\N{\b0\fs12}a ride into town is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,專攻政治社會學的22歲學生\N{\b0\fs12}a 22-year-old poly sci major at SCU,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他還加入了一個兄弟會\N{\b0\fs12}and a member of gamma tau,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這就能解釋\N{\b0\fs12}which totally explains the whole
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道在幫助並教唆一名重犯的戲碼了\N{\b0\fs12}"I didn't know I was aiding and abetting a known felon" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,只要是女的就能讓兄弟會的人做任何事\N{\b0\fs12}Anyone with boobs can get a frat boy to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-我曾經是兄弟會成員  -我不說了\N{\b0\fs12}- I was a frat boy. - I rest my case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,至少她沒殺他  還不錯\N{\b0\fs12}At least she didn't kill him. That's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼克制不是海倫娜的風格\N{\b0\fs12}It's not like Helena to show restraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,聽上去你好像很瞭解她啊\N{\b0\fs12}It sounds like you have a type.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續注意員警的動向\N{\b0\fs12}Keep tabs on the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果警方有她的線索  馬上通知我\N{\b0\fs12}Let me know if they get any leads on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找幾個線人問問\N{\b0\fs12}I'll do some canvassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-你還好嗎  -還好\N{\b0\fs12}- You OK? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,明天這個時候  就會像什麼都沒發生過了\N{\b0\fs12}By this time tomorrow, it'll be like nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那是米拉庫魯的優點之一\N{\b0\fs12}That's one upside to Mirakuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一的優點\N{\b0\fs12}The only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你打算說什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Look, I know what you're going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨晚已經控制得很好了\N{\b0\fs12}I had it under control last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  好到我差點就又射你一箭了\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, so under control that I almost put another arrow in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經打算後退了  但你不給我機會\N{\b0\fs12}I was going to back off, but you never gave me a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一讓你迅速清醒的事\N{\b0\fs12}The only thing that snapped you out of it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我提起西婭\N{\b0\fs12}was when I brought up Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你沖我喊我閃電的原因\N{\b0\fs12}That's why you called me Speedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我以為你想給我起個昵稱\N{\b0\fs12}I--I thought you were trying to give me a nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但我要聲明  別叫我閃電\N{\b0\fs12}But for the record, don't call me Speedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,記住了\N{\b0\fs12}Noted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  你是個危險的人\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, you're dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為我是在幫你控制它\N{\b0\fs12}I thought I was helping you control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你是的  我是說\N{\b0\fs12}You are. I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到一碗水就忍不住去拍它\N{\b0\fs12}I can't look at a bowl of water without slapping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,數周以來你第一次出外勤\N{\b0\fs12}The first time that you're out in the field in weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你就  準備好殺人了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}and...you're ready to kill somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這可不行\N{\b0\fs12}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起  我幾個月前就應該讓你這麼做的\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry, I should have asked you to do this months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,做什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Asked me to do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,遠離西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Stay away from Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我  我做不到\N{\b0\fs12}No, I--I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,她在你身邊的時候非常不安全\N{\b0\fs12}She's not safe when she's around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你生氣失控時\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not sure anybody is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,誰在你身邊都不安全\N{\b0\fs12}when you lose yourself to this rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你愛她\N{\b0\fs12}You love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你要按我說的做\N{\b0\fs12}And that's why you're going to do what I'm asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,太驚人了\N{\b0\fs12}Such a big uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,海倫娜\N{\b0\fs12}Helena?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,檢察官亞當•唐納宣佈\N{\b0\fs12}ADA Adam Donner announced
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在短暫的休假之後勞蕾爾•蘭斯\N{\b0\fs12}the return of Laurel Lance to the D.A.'s office
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,正式回歸地方檢察官辦公室\N{\b0\fs12}after a brief sabbatical.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}重大新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她將主導對波提納爾的起訴\N{\b0\fs12}She will lead the prosecution of Mr. Bertinelli.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,陪審團的選定從今天開始\N{\b0\fs12}Jury selection starts today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你來這裡做什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我從新聞上得知你拿到了幾個大案子\N{\b0\fs12}I heard you picked up some big new case on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼不給我打電話\N{\b0\fs12}How come you didn't call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我想打的  但一切都發生的太快了\N{\b0\fs12}I was going to, but it all happened so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,再說  我覺得你和爸爸不會讓我\N{\b0\fs12}Plus, I thought you and dad would try and talk me out of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼快就重新開始工作\N{\b0\fs12}going back to work so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是為這個來的\N{\b0\fs12}Which is why you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我很擔心你\N{\b0\fs12}I'm just worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你擔心我會犯錯誤\N{\b0\fs12}If you're worried I'm going to slip,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天依然要參加兩場會議  而且\N{\b0\fs12}I'm still going to two meetings a day, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  不是指那個\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都知道波提納爾是個什麼貨色\N{\b0\fs12}Everybody knows what kind of guy Bertinelli is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,更不用說他那個已經準備回星城來\N{\b0\fs12}And not to mention his completely psychotic daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,殺掉他的精神病女兒\N{\b0\fs12}who's already on her way back to Starling City to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道的\N{\b0\fs12}How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:11:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\b0\fs12}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是希望你安全\N{\b0\fs12}I just want you to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛你的體貼\N{\b0\fs12}And I love you for caring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是莎拉  你從來沒見過我當律師\N{\b0\fs12}But Sara, you've never seen me be a lawyer before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很擅長這份工作\N{\b0\fs12}And I am really good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很懷念\N{\b0\fs12}And I miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了\N{\b0\fs12}I have to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,庭審可不能遲到\N{\b0\fs12}I can't be late for court.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡真是比貨船好多了啊\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, this is much better than the freighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,亨德里克  你喜歡在船上的話可以遊回去\N{\b0\fs12}You prefer boat, Hendrik, feel free to swim back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉說奧利弗在這活了一年多\N{\b0\fs12}Sara said Oliver survived here for over a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也可以的\N{\b0\fs12}We can do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,除非艾沃和他的手下找到我們\N{\b0\fs12}Unless Ivo and his men come find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不知道船上發生了什麼\N{\b0\fs12}We don't know what happened on the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,誰還活著  誰已經死了\N{\b0\fs12}Who's alive and who's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉  你在嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Sara, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德  奧利弗...\N{\b0\fs12}Slade! Is Oliver...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他很痛苦  是的\N{\b0\fs12}He's in pain, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但他現在依然活著\N{\b0\fs12}But he's still breathing--for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德  聽著  你贏了  行了吧  \N{\b0\fs12}Slade, listen, you won, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,亞馬遜號歸你了\N{\b0\fs12}You have the "Amazo."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,放了奧利弗吧  你可以把我們留在這裡\N{\b0\fs12}Just let Oliver go, and then you can leave us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我的問題  莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Well, here's my problem, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我走不了\N{\b0\fs12}I can't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-為什麼  -我們交火的時候\N{\b0\fs12}- Why not? - During our assault,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,船的發動機損壞了\N{\b0\fs12}the ship's engine was damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,無法航行了\N{\b0\fs12}She won't sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,很不幸交火時我還把工程師殺了\N{\b0\fs12}During the attack, unfortunately I decapitated the engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以怎麼處理我們的問題呢  莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}So what can we do about our problem, Sara?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要奧利弗回去\N{\b0\fs12}You want Oliver back,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,而我需要一個有能力修船的人\N{\b0\fs12}and I need someone qualified to fix this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,為了奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}For Oliver's sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望亨德里克先生跟你在一起\N{\b0\fs12}I sure hope a Mr. Hendrik is there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,非致命的箭\N{\b0\fs12}Non-lethal arrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,玩這種小孩的玩意可不是你的風格\N{\b0\fs12}It's not like you to play with kid gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊怎麼樣了\N{\b0\fs12}How's Roy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,跟海倫娜一樣  他不太喜歡我作為導師的技巧\N{\b0\fs12}Like Helena, he is not too pleased with my skills as a mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾不願放棄那案子\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel won't drop the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,她現在就在去法庭的路上\N{\b0\fs12}She's headed to court right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-你要去哪兒  -去法庭\N{\b0\fs12}- Where are you going? - To the courthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘帶你的小孩子箭頭了\N{\b0\fs12}Well, hey, you forgot your baby arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白你那套不殺人的主張\N{\b0\fs12}Look, I get your whole no killing spree,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果最後要救勞蕾爾  殺掉海倫娜\N{\b0\fs12}but if it comes down to saving Laurel or killing Helena--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉  並不只有這兩個選擇\N{\b0\fs12}Sara, those aren't the only two choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德威脅你的家人的時候\N{\b0\fs12}Well, you were happy enough to let Dig take the kill shot
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你也高興地讓狄格下了殺手\N{\b0\fs12}when it was Slade threatening your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這不一樣\N{\b0\fs12}This is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我辜負了海倫娜\N{\b0\fs12}I failed Helena.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"女殺手"是我創造出來的\N{\b0\fs12}I created the "Huntress".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  斯萊德也是你創造出來的\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, well, you created Slade, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你說得對\N{\b0\fs12}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你說得對\N{\b0\fs12}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但一旦涉及我們的家人\N{\b0\fs12}But when it comes to our families...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我們倆頭腦就都不清楚\N{\b0\fs12}neither one of us thinks clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你得留在這裡\N{\b0\fs12}Which is why you have to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利\N{\b0\fs12}Ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能留下\N{\b0\fs12}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓勞蕾爾出任何事的\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not going to let anything happen to Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我也愛她\N{\b0\fs12}I love her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你們覺得呢\N{\b0\fs12}What do you guys think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得如果"女殺手"出現\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, I think if the Huntress shows up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該打爆她\N{\b0\fs12}you should totally kick her ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託別告訴我你也很擔心我\N{\b0\fs12}Please don't tell me you're worried about me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是  我只是想看看審判\N{\b0\fs12}No, I just wanted to watch the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽說那個律師很特別\N{\b0\fs12}I heard the prosecutor was something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪\N{\b0\fs12}That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他們為什麼帶他從正門進來\N{\b0\fs12}Why are they bringing him in through the front entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都趴下\N{\b0\fs12}Everybody get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊  爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}Hi, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我來晚了  你可真不好找啊\N{\b0\fs12}Sorry I'm late, but you're a hard man to track down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但你回到星城很合適\N{\b0\fs12}But it's fitting that you came back to Starling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這是一切開始的地方\N{\b0\fs12}Where it all began.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是你殺了邁克爾的地方\N{\b0\fs12}Where you killed Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我差一點就為你感到抱歉了\N{\b0\fs12}You know, I almost feel sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,海倫娜\N{\b0\fs12}Helena...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:15:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\b0\fs12}Stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  你知道我不能\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver, you know I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那你還在等什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Well, what are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我說  你還在等什麼\N{\b0\fs12}I said, what are you waiting for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,海倫娜•波提納爾  把武器放下\N{\b0\fs12}Helena Bertinelli, put down your weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,把手舉過頭頂\N{\b0\fs12}and place your hands above your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼說這是一個大陷阱...\N{\b0\fs12}So this was a big trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是誘餌\N{\b0\fs12}with you as the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他們給你什麼好處\N{\b0\fs12}What did they offer you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他們什麼好處也不用給我\N{\b0\fs12}Ah, they didn't have to offer me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,放棄吧  波提納爾女士  大樓被包圍了\N{\b0\fs12}Give up, Miss Bertinelli, the building's surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都怎麼教導我的來著  爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}What was it you always taught me, daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,做好萬全的準備\N{\b0\fs12}Be prepared for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,動手\N{\b0\fs12}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住人質  後退\N{\b0\fs12}Take hostages, and fall back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,別開槍  別開槍  他們手裡有人質\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, hold your fire, hold your fire! They have hostages!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,別開槍  重復  別開槍  他們有人質\N{\b0\fs12}Hold fire. Say it again, hold fire. They've taken hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾在哪兒  勞蕾爾在哪兒  她跟你一起嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Where's Laurel? Where's Laurel? Is she with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  蘭斯先生  我們走散了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry, Mr. Lance, we got separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她還在裡面\N{\b0\fs12}She's still inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我們正在星城法院外進行直播\N{\b0\fs12}We are live outside the Starling City courthouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,海倫娜•波提納爾和不明數量的攻擊者\N{\b0\fs12}where Helena Bertinelli and an unknown number of assailants
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,控制了整棟大樓\N{\b0\fs12}seized control of the entire building.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我被告知\N{\b0\fs12}And I'm now being told,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在裡面控制了一些人質\N{\b0\fs12}they are holding a number of hostages inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,安排狙擊手帶著熱成像瞄準鏡\N{\b0\fs12}I want snipers with thermals on top
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在兩個街區範圍內的所有大樓頂部待命\N{\b0\fs12}of every building for a two block radius.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不應該發生這種事的  上尉\N{\b0\fs12}This was not how it was supposed to go down, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟我保證說不會有傷亡的\N{\b0\fs12}You promised me there wouldn't be any casualties!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你的主意嗎  你這個混蛋\N{\b0\fs12}This was your idea, huh? You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我女兒在裡面\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, my daughter's in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你們是怎麼想的\N{\b0\fs12}What were you guys thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,拿那麼多無辜的生命冒險\N{\b0\fs12}putting all those innocent lives at risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-聽著  我是在執行命令  -命令\N{\b0\fs12}- Listen! I was following orders. - Orders?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,波提納爾女士\N{\b0\fs12}Ms. Bertinelli.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,任何人都不必死\N{\b0\fs12}No one has to die today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸需要死\N{\b0\fs12}My father does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你們把他交給我\N{\b0\fs12}And unless you hand him over to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我要開始殺人質了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm going to start killing hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧  唐納先生\N{\b0\fs12}See this, Mr. Donner,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是你不管戴面具的瘋子的後果\N{\b0\fs12}is what happens when you let freaks with masks run wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,把他們帶出去\N{\b0\fs12}Get them the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,別碰我\N{\b0\fs12}Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是我媽打來的\N{\b0\fs12}It's my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,警探\N{\b0\fs12}Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,海倫娜•波提納爾控制了十名人質\N{\b0\fs12}Helena Bertinelli just took ten hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾就是其中之一\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel's one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道現在的情況\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, I'm aware of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  你在哪裡  你還好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver, where are you? Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我以奧利弗的身份和蘭斯在一起\N{\b0\fs12}I'm with Lance as Oliver,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他剛剛打給綠箭俠了\N{\b0\fs12}and he just called the Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越難搞清\N{\b0\fs12}It's getting really hard to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:19:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道誰的秘密身份了\N{\b0\fs12}keep track of who knows whose secret identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,費利西蒂  勞蕾爾還在法院裡\N{\b0\fs12}Felicity, Laurel is still inside the courthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要什麼  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}What do you need, Oliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-我的戰袍  -這就來\N{\b0\fs12}- My work clothes. - I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,讓莎拉接電話\N{\b0\fs12}Put Sara on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她不在這裡\N{\b0\fs12}She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,她去哪了\N{\b0\fs12}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你是好人嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you one of the good guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不  但我和好人是朋友\N{\b0\fs12}No, but I'm friends with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}威登酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-看著點  -去你的\N{\b0\fs12}- Dude, watch it. - Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭  我們分手吧\N{\b0\fs12}Thea, we need to break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\b0\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不要是什麼意思\N{\b0\fs12}What do you mean, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭  我要和你分手\N{\b0\fs12}Thea, I'm breaking up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不行\N{\b0\fs12}No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能強迫我和你約會\N{\b0\fs12}You can't make me date you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  昨天你才用全部積蓄\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, yesterday you gave me a bracelet
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,買了個手鐲送給我\N{\b0\fs12}worth every dime that you had,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,現在卻要和我分手了\N{\b0\fs12}And now what, you want to end things?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你最近顯然不太好過\N{\b0\fs12}Look, you're clearly going through something right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓你一個人撐著的\N{\b0\fs12}and I'm not going to let you go through it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我會永遠陪著你\N{\b0\fs12}I'm always going to be here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.91,0:20:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  西婭  私人派對那個男的\N{\b0\fs12}Sorry, Thea. The guy from the private party
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,說我們上錯了伏特加  在發飆呢\N{\b0\fs12}said we stocked the wrong vodka, and he's freaking me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們待會再談  好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Look, we'll talk about this later, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.27,0:21:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你受傷了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我太笨了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你不會想那麼做的\N{\b0\fs12}You don't want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, no, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要\N{\b0\fs12}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那你的戒酒的事怎麼辦\N{\b0\fs12}What about your sobriety?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道的\N{\b0\fs12}How do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你鑰匙圈上的那個"A"\N{\b0\fs12}The "A" chip on your keychain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,30天\N{\b0\fs12}30 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}戒酒30天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我今天為什麼會來嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you even know why I'm here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,原來我就是個裝飾\N{\b0\fs12}Turns out I'm decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可有可無的裝飾\N{\b0\fs12}Expendable decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼意思\N{\b0\fs12}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,整個庭審就是個幌子\N{\b0\fs12}This whole trial was a sham.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我早該想到的\N{\b0\fs12}I should have seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉是對的\N{\b0\fs12}Sara was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉是\N{\b0\fs12}Sara, she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我妹妹\N{\b0\fs12}she's my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她說我還沒有準備好\N{\b0\fs12}She said that I wasn't ready to come back, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為那是她保護過度\N{\b0\fs12}I just thought she was being overprotective.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,姐妹之間總是這樣\N{\b0\fs12}Well, sisters can be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你真該見見我的姐妹\N{\b0\fs12}You should meet mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她受了很多苦\N{\b0\fs12}She's gone through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她一定很堅強\N{\b0\fs12}She must have been so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是\N{\b0\fs12}I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我想讓她和我自己看到\N{\b0\fs12}I wanted to show her, show myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.80,0:22:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我也依然很堅強\N{\b0\fs12}that I was still strong, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.30,0:22:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那展現給我看吧\N{\b0\fs12}So show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走\N{\b0\fs12}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.74,0:22:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在裡面  我找到勞蕾爾•蘭斯了\N{\b0\fs12}Inside. I've got Laurel Lance,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.36,0:22:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她沒事\N{\b0\fs12}she's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.79,0:22:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是綠箭俠嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is that the Arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我在向南側的出口走\N{\b0\fs12}I'm headed to an egress point in the south wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\b0\fs12}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:22:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人質怎麼辦\N{\b0\fs12}What about the other hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你就放著他們不管了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You're just going to leave them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.91,0:23:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我得救你出去\N{\b0\fs12}Look, I need to get you to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白  我有什麼特殊的\N{\b0\fs12}I don't understand! What is so special about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.78,0:23:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她不願意走\N{\b0\fs12}She won't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我瞭解海倫娜\N{\b0\fs12}I know Helena.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.33,0:23:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她會把他們都殺了的\N{\b0\fs12}She's going to kill all of those people,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那些無辜的人\N{\b0\fs12}innocent people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是你讓我展現自己的堅強\N{\b0\fs12}You wanted me to show you I'm strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在就給你看  我要留下來\N{\b0\fs12}This is me being strong. I'm staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底要不要幫我\N{\b0\fs12}Are you going to help me or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.30,0:23:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,快把她帶出來\N{\b0\fs12}Get her out of there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.73,0:23:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我又不能直接把她打暈\N{\b0\fs12}It's not like I can just knock her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.98,0:23:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想你和海倫娜交鋒\N{\b0\fs12}I don't want you engaging Helena.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼  你是怕她會做什麼嗎\N{\b0\fs12}What, you're afraid of what she'll do...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,還是我會做什麼事\N{\b0\fs12}or what I'll do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉  你不是個殺手\N{\b0\fs12}Sara...you're not a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我該是什麼就是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}I am what I need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉  你能聽到嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Sara, did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽得到\N{\b0\fs12}I heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.81,0:23:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,亨德里克不在\N{\b0\fs12}Hendrik's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.81,0:23:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有人想跟你打個招呼\N{\b0\fs12}There's someone I'd like you to say hello to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.34,0:23:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都別給他  莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Don't give him anything, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利\N{\b0\fs12}Ollie!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,最後一次機會\N{\b0\fs12}One last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.58,0:24:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗換亨德里克\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver for Hendrik.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.46,0:24:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我說過了  亨德里克沒有\N{\b0\fs12}I told you! Look, Hendrik, he didn't make it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.45,0:24:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,活著到島上  他淹死了\N{\b0\fs12}to the island, he drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.51,0:24:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,想想一年前  你不過是個大學女孩\N{\b0\fs12}To think it was only a year ago, you were a little college girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.53,0:24:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,繞著男生轉\N{\b0\fs12}fretting about boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.23,0:24:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼意思\N{\b0\fs12}What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.07,0:24:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你可不會騙人\N{\b0\fs12}You're not a good liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.51,0:24:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德  求你  住手\N{\b0\fs12}Slade! Stop, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.96,0:24:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他是你的朋友\N{\b0\fs12}Look, he's your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.24,0:24:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛就是電流穿過我朋友的聲音\N{\b0\fs12}That is the sound of electricity surging through my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.22,0:24:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,準確來說是5毫安培\N{\b0\fs12}Five milliamps, to be exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.28,0:24:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,7毫安培能使心臟停跳\N{\b0\fs12}Seven causes cardiac arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.90,0:24:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗剛才在6毫安培的時候暈過去了\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver just passed out with six milliamps.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.20,0:24:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一小時後如果亨德里克沒被帶到我面前\N{\b0\fs12}He'll be delivered with the fatal blow of seven
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.34,0:24:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我就用7毫安培送他上路\N{\b0\fs12}in one hour if hendrik is not standing here by my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.02,0:24:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我死也不會回去的\N{\b0\fs12}There's no way in hell I'm going back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.08,0:25:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我有次差點結婚了\N{\b0\fs12}I was almost married once.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.32,0:25:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,已經過了一小時了\N{\b0\fs12}It's been an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.53,0:25:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是說話算話的\N{\b0\fs12}and I'm a woman of my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.87,0:25:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不信問我爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}Just ask my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.35,0:25:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,會沒事的\N{\b0\fs12}Everything's going to be ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.00,0:25:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小心後面\N{\b0\fs12}Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.42,0:25:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗真的很喜歡讓他的女朋友變裝\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver sure does like to dress up his girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.06,0:26:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.88,0:26:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾她還在那\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel! She's still in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.19,0:26:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,很高興再次見到你  勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Nice to see you again, Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.54,0:26:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,海倫娜  聽我說\N{\b0\fs12}Helena, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.47,0:26:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-這一切必須結束  -我同意\N{\b0\fs12}- This has to end. - I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.82,0:26:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我父親被裝進棺材就結束\N{\b0\fs12}And it ends with my father in a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.25,0:26:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,員警不會把你父親交出來的\N{\b0\fs12}The police are never going to hand over your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.74,0:26:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  他們不會\N{\b0\fs12}No, they won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.29,0:26:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以要由你把他交給我\N{\b0\fs12}That's why you're going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.05,0:26:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,很簡單\N{\b0\fs12}Simple trade--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.05,0:26:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,用我父親來交換勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}my father for Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.59,0:27:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}威登酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.37,0:27:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,夥計們\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.50,0:27:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還需要一些伏特加\N{\b0\fs12}We need more vodka.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.39,0:27:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\b0\fs12}Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.37,0:27:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己去拿\N{\b0\fs12}I'll get it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.15,0:27:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你們要帶我去哪兒\N{\b0\fs12}Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.97,0:27:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,安全屋\N{\b0\fs12}Safe house.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.82,0:27:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著  正門被記者的圍攻了\N{\b0\fs12}Listen, front's mobbed with reporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.57,0:27:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,把波提納爾從後門帶出去\N{\b0\fs12}Let's take Bertinelli out the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.71,0:27:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,把車開過來\N{\b0\fs12}Bring the van around.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.66,0:27:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\b0\fs12}Ow! All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.55,0:27:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎麼回事  -別怕\N{\b0\fs12}- Whoa! What the hell? - Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.65,0:27:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-到底怎麼回事  -快上車\N{\b0\fs12}- What's going on? - Just get in the van!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.27,0:28:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,特警隊已經做好準備闖進法院\N{\b0\fs12}SWAT's getting ready to breach the courthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.22,0:28:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們現在就去換人\N{\b0\fs12}Then we make the trade now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.40,0:28:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著  我可不會因為弗蘭克死了而失眠\N{\b0\fs12}Listen, I'm not going to lose any sleep over Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.80,0:28:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你要把他交給他女兒嗎\N{\b0\fs12}But are you really going to serve him up to his daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.65,0:28:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.66,0:28:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚誰也不會死\N{\b0\fs12}No one dies tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.95,0:28:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.16,0:28:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,會沒事的\N{\b0\fs12}Everything's going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.18,0:28:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我說過  不許講話\N{\b0\fs12}I said...no talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.40,0:28:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我們那天晚上談過\N{\b0\fs12}We talked that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.13,0:28:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你  奧利弗  湯米和我\N{\b0\fs12}You, Oliver, Tommy, and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.21,0:28:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,吃晚飯的時候\N{\b0\fs12}At dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.14,0:28:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得你說你的未婚夫被殺了\N{\b0\fs12}I remember you telling me your fiance was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.32,0:28:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很遺憾\N{\b0\fs12}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.61,0:28:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你這麼說我們就是好朋友了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Does this make us girlfriends?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.73,0:28:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.40,0:28:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我明白失去一個人的滋味\N{\b0\fs12}But I know what it's like to lose someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.11,0:28:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可憐的勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Poor Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.29,0:28:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,湯米把你甩了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Did Tommy dump you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.47,0:28:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有\N{\b0\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.90,0:29:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\b0\fs12}He died.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.94,0:29:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我始終放不下這件事\N{\b0\fs12}And I couldn't deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.41,0:29:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我開始酗酒\N{\b0\fs12}So I became a drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.18,0:29:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,每當遇到問題\N{\b0\fs12}Every problem I had,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.63,0:29:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我就用藥片或者酒精來解決\N{\b0\fs12}I solved with a pill or a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.01,0:29:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我的朋友和家人們都試圖幫我\N{\b0\fs12}My friends and my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.52,0:29:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但我據他們千里之外\N{\b0\fs12}they tried to help me, but I wouldn't let them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.52,0:29:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必這麼做的  海倫娜\N{\b0\fs12}You don't have to do this, Helena.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.46,0:29:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,現在還不算太晚\N{\b0\fs12}It's not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.09,0:29:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要這麼做\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.35,0:29:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦黑暗駐進了你的內心\N{\b0\fs12}Because once you let the darkness inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.76,0:29:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,它就永遠不會出去了\N{\b0\fs12}it never comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.26,0:29:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,海倫娜  你父親在我這\N{\b0\fs12}Helena. I have your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.89,0:29:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要一個四人小組  鑽石陣型\N{\b0\fs12}I want four men teams, diamond formations.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.45,0:29:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,快速移動  精確狙擊\N{\b0\fs12}Move fast, shoot sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.57,0:29:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,還有一件事  治安維持者不是法律\N{\b0\fs12}One more thing-- vigilantes are not the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.66,0:29:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他們帶著面具出現  就給他們一槍\N{\b0\fs12}If they're wearing a mask, they get a bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.44,0:30:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,開始行動\N{\b0\fs12}Let's move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.85,0:30:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,波提納爾立刻把手舉起來\N{\b0\fs12}Hands up, bertinelli! Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.87,0:30:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你別殺我  求求你\N{\b0\fs12}Please don't kill me! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.18,0:30:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,她告訴我\N{\b0\fs12}She--she told me--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.86,0:30:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不穿上它  她就殺了我\N{\b0\fs12}She told me to wear it or she'd kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.79,0:30:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,她在哪\N{\b0\fs12}Where the hell is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.39,0:30:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,別那麼害怕  勞蕾爾  你或許能活下來呢\N{\b0\fs12}Don't look so scared, Laurel. You might just live through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.01,0:30:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你們要把我交到我女兒手裡嗎\N{\b0\fs12}So you're just going to hand me over to my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.20,0:30:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為你們是好人\N{\b0\fs12}I thought you were the good guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.48,0:30:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴\N{\b0\fs12}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.85,0:30:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,還記得我說過關於克制的事嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Remember all that stuff I said about restraint?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.33,0:30:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,忘了吧\N{\b0\fs12}Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.47,0:30:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能通過變成海倫娜那樣的人來阻止她\N{\b0\fs12}You can't stop someone like Helena by becoming her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.41,0:30:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣能保護我愛的人  我就怎樣做\N{\b0\fs12}I'll do what I have to to protect someone I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.13,0:31:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,亨德里克  拜託  把槍放下\N{\b0\fs12}Hendrik, please, put the gun down!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.03,0:31:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼  那樣你就可以把我送回那個地獄去了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Why? So you can send me back to that hell hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.21,0:31:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不這樣想\N{\b0\fs12}I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.92,0:31:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我們任何人都不能決定我們之中誰活誰死\N{\b0\fs12}It's not for any of us to decide who lives and dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.14,0:31:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但亨德里克這種情況  我願意破例一次\N{\b0\fs12}But in Hendrik's case, I'd be willing to make an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.41,0:31:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我要離開這  別阻止我\N{\b0\fs12}I'm leaving. Don't stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.62,0:31:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,說得倒好  你是不會開槍殺我的\N{\b0\fs12}Good at talking, but you will not kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.13,0:31:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就試試\N{\b0\fs12}Let's find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.70,0:31:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,長官  我們收到蘭斯女士手機的信號了\N{\b0\fs12}Sir, we've got a ping off Ms. Lance's cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.86,0:31:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她一定帶著電話\N{\b0\fs12}She must still have it on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.36,0:31:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.31,0:31:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在蓋爾街和西蒙街交匯的一個機械商店裡\N{\b0\fs12}A machine shop at Gail street and Simone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.39,0:31:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,需要我們趕過去嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Should we rally up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.60,0:31:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要  留守在你們的位置\N{\b0\fs12}Negative. Hold your location.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.26,0:31:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  長官\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.85,0:31:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,警官  在這裡好好鎮守\N{\b0\fs12}Sergeant, keep this position.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.33,0:31:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,對你來說真諷刺啊  爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}Well, this is irony for you, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.30,0:32:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,吉米•戴戈斯諾的屍體\N{\b0\fs12}Didn't you have Jimmy D'agostino's body
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.00,0:32:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就被你埋在隔壁的地下吧\N{\b0\fs12}buried under the building next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.03,0:32:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  女兒\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry, my girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.93,0:32:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你就要死了  我肯定你的確抱歉\N{\b0\fs12}Now you're about to die, I'm sure you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.04,0:32:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.86,0:32:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我是對那個我曾經帶著去芭蕾課的小女孩抱歉\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry for that little girl i used to take to ballet class.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.22,0:32:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去滑雪旅行的小女孩\N{\b0\fs12}Go on ski trips with.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.65,0:32:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾幫著做數學作業的小女孩\N{\b0\fs12}The one I used to help with her math homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.25,0:32:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她討厭數學\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, she hated math.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.36,0:32:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我為她帶來了這麼多傷害\N{\b0\fs12}Sorry that I caused her so much hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.38,0:32:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,而她帶給我如此多的歡樂\N{\b0\fs12}'cause she brought me so much joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.78,0:32:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,海倫娜\N{\b0\fs12}Helena!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.02,0:32:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不要殺他\N{\b0\fs12}Don't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.92,0:32:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣你就再也回不去了\N{\b0\fs12}You can never come back from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.98,0:32:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,太晚了\N{\b0\fs12}It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.95,0:32:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經回不去了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.80,0:32:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,再見  爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}Bye, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.79,0:32:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡的治安維持者\N{\b0\fs12}Damn vigilantes!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.53,0:32:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你們觸犯了法律\N{\b0\fs12}You went above the law!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.23,0:33:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,上次出現這種情況時  我把你從窗戶扔了出去\N{\b0\fs12}Last time this happened, I threw you out a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.76,0:33:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我當時有所保留呢\N{\b0\fs12}I was holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.21,0:33:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這次不會了\N{\b0\fs12}I won't do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.72,0:34:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.25,0:34:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是殺人犯\N{\b0\fs12}You're not a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.16,0:34:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不知道真正的我是什麼樣子  勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}You don't know who I am, Laurel, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.75,0:34:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那就展現給我看\N{\b0\fs12}Then show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.07,0:34:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs12}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.62,0:34:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是我的\N{\b0\fs12}It was supposed to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.06,0:34:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是我來動手的\N{\b0\fs12}It was supposed to me who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.56,0:34:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,行了  波提納爾  夠了\N{\b0\fs12}All right, Bertinelli, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.29,0:34:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\b0\fs12}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.15,0:35:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼進來的\N{\b0\fs12}How did you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.30,0:35:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我們家族為員警的退休基本捐了一大筆錢\N{\b0\fs12}My family makes a generous donation to the policemen's retirement fund.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.00,0:35:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我偶爾會讓他們幫個小忙\N{\b0\fs12}And every once in a while, I get to call in a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.15,0:35:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那你應該讓他們把我\N{\b0\fs12}Hmm. Maybe you could ask them to send me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.06,0:35:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,送去熱帶的監獄\N{\b0\fs12}to prison somewhere tropical.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.06,0:35:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為我的感覺會有所不同\N{\b0\fs12}You know, I thought I'd feel different.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.26,0:35:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但他死後  我的感覺沒變\N{\b0\fs12}Now that he's dead, but I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.77,0:35:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直跟我說\N{\b0\fs12}And you always told me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.45,0:35:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,殺了他也無濟於事\N{\b0\fs12}killing him wouldn't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.22,0:35:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你說得對\N{\b0\fs12}You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.24,0:35:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我也有錯\N{\b0\fs12}But I was wrong, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.99,0:35:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼錯了\N{\b0\fs12}About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.56,0:35:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為我能幫你\N{\b0\fs12}I thought I could help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.06,0:35:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,能阻止你殺人\N{\b0\fs12}Stop you from being a killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.63,0:35:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\b0\fs12}but...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.90,0:35:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我才剛剛開始\N{\b0\fs12}I was just starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.62,0:36:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前也是個殺人犯\N{\b0\fs12}And I was a killer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.65,0:36:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那現在呢\N{\b0\fs12}And what are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.63,0:36:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我在努力變好\N{\b0\fs12}I'm trying to be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.49,0:36:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很蠢  但是\N{\b0\fs12}It's so stupid, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.71,0:36:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想  既然他死了\N{\b0\fs12}I keep thinking, now that he's dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.95,0:36:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我父親和邁克爾在一起了  而我...\N{\b0\fs12}my father and Michael are together, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.70,0:36:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我仍然在這裡\N{\b0\fs12}I'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.15,0:36:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,孤身一人\N{\b0\fs12}Alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.65,0:36:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是孤身一人\N{\b0\fs12}You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.75,0:37:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你在對我做什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are you doing to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.10,0:37:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,羅馬時期\N{\b0\fs12}In Roman times,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.25,0:37:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,罪犯會被做上標記\N{\b0\fs12}a criminal was branded
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.28,0:37:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,以讓世人分辨出他的罪行\N{\b0\fs12}to identify his crimes to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.61,0:37:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也永遠提醒他自己的所作所為\N{\b0\fs12}and to forever remind him of what he'd done.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.36,0:37:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,莎朵的背上就有這個紋身\N{\b0\fs12}Shado wore this tattoo on her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.26,0:37:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你的餘生就一直背負著這個紋身吧\N{\b0\fs12}Now you shall wear it for the rest of your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.73,0:37:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不論你的生命有多麼短暫\N{\b0\fs12}however short that may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.97,0:37:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,弗林\N{\b0\fs12}Flynn.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.87,0:37:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,弗林\N{\b0\fs12}Flynn.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.40,0:37:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Hello, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.64,0:37:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你做出了正確的選擇\N{\b0\fs12}I hope you've made the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.53,0:37:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\b0\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.89,0:37:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我代表整個地檢辦辦公室\N{\b0\fs12}Look, on behalf of the entire DA's office,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.26,0:37:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,向你道歉\N{\b0\fs12}I have to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.40,0:38:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,亞當•唐納已經不在這裡工作了\N{\b0\fs12}Adam Donner's employment here has been terminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.50,0:38:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我們之前真的不知道他有什麼陰謀詭計\N{\b0\fs12}Obviously we had no idea what he was plotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.02,0:38:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但願如此\N{\b0\fs12}I would hope not.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.96,0:38:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,很不幸  亞當沒有權利\N{\b0\fs12}Unfortunately, Adam was not authorized
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.89,0:38:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你回來工作\N{\b0\fs12}to offer you your job back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.27,0:38:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.92,0:38:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是一切都沒變\N{\b0\fs12}but nothing has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.20,0:38:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不  變了\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.29,0:38:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.30,0:38:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你要把工作還給我  凱特\N{\b0\fs12}You are going to rehire me, Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.36,0:38:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你想去向媒體解釋\N{\b0\fs12}Unless you feel like explaining to the press
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.92,0:38:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,自己手下的區助理檢察官\N{\b0\fs12}that your own assistant district attorney
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.56,0:38:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就是今晚人質危機事件的幕後黑手\N{\b0\fs12}was the brilliant mastermind behind tonight's hostage crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.11,0:38:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來\N{\b0\fs12}Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.23,0:38:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不得不說  真讓我刮目相看啊\N{\b0\fs12}I have to say, I am impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.65,0:38:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為你不會用威脅這麼骯臟的手段\N{\b0\fs12}I would have thought blackmail was a little dark for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.68,0:38:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,最近有人告訴我\N{\b0\fs12}Someone recently told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.66,0:38:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦讓黑暗駐進自己的內心\N{\b0\fs12}once you let the darkness inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.06,0:39:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,它就永遠不會出去了\N{\b0\fs12}it never comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.98,0:39:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}威登酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.14,0:39:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你還在這裡幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are you still doing up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.92,0:39:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,思考\N{\b0\fs12}Thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.66,0:39:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哭泣\N{\b0\fs12}Crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.11,0:39:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我和羅伊...\N{\b0\fs12}Roy and I are...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.14,0:39:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.20,0:39:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我抓到他跟一個賤人一起\N{\b0\fs12}I caught him with some slut.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.12,0:39:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那邊\N{\b0\fs12}Right over there, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.25,0:39:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我很遺憾\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.62,0:39:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他那樣做是為了把我推開\N{\b0\fs12}He was doing it to push me away,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.53,0:39:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這下起作用了\N{\b0\fs12}which clearly worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.27,0:39:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我不知道為什麼\N{\b0\fs12}I just... I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.80,0:39:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼大家說實話\N{\b0\fs12}Why is it so hard for everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.59,0:40:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就那麼難呢\N{\b0\fs12}just to tell the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.22,0:40:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊根本就不跟我說實話\N{\b0\fs12}I mean, Roy can't even tell me the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.11,0:40:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不告訴我到底為什麼跟我分手\N{\b0\fs12}of why he wants to end things with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.58,0:40:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽  她...\N{\b0\fs12}Mom, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.17,0:40:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,她守著那麼多秘密\N{\b0\fs12}She keeps all of these secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.74,0:40:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你...\N{\b0\fs12}I mean, doesn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.28,0:40:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你不覺得她還有什麼瞞著我們嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Doesn't it feel like she's still keeping something from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.81,0:40:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道  西婭\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know, Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.69,0:40:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你是唯一一個不撒謊騙我的  奧利\N{\b0\fs12}You're the only one that doesn't lie to me, Ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.85,0:40:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我認識的人中\N{\b0\fs12}You're the only one I know
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.88,0:40:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一一個不瞞著我的\N{\b0\fs12}who doesn't keep secrets from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.80,0:40:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走了\N{\b0\fs12}Just, I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.30,0:40:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我開車送你吧\N{\b0\fs12}Let me drive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.18,0:40:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了  我現在想一個人靜一靜\N{\b0\fs12}No, I just want to be alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.95,0:40:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她沒事吧\N{\b0\fs12}Is she OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.05,0:40:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,會沒事的\N{\b0\fs12}She will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.75,0:41:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,最終會的\N{\b0\fs12}Eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.42,0:41:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你今晚做得很棒\N{\b0\fs12}You did good tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.94,0:41:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,英雄都會那樣做的  對嗎\N{\b0\fs12}That's what heroes do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.25,0:41:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這是個危險的城市\N{\b0\fs12}It's a dangerous city.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.22,0:41:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你不該一個人在街上的\N{\b0\fs12}You shouldn't be out in the streets alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.18,0:41:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,威爾遜先生\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Wilson?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.87,0:41:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我斯萊德就行\N{\b0\fs12}Please. Call me Slade.